trans-unit.source: Iterates over all the content-typed nodes which precede the starting node in document order.
trans-unit.target: 문서 순서로 시작 노드 앞에 있는 모든 내용을 입력 한 노드를 반복 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns nodes in reverse document order.
The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: 경우에만 탐색기 변경의 상태는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A>메서드가 반환 되었음을 `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: The node from which you start traversing the nodes.
An instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"></xref> class, which enables you to filter nodes based on the name.
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스는 <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"> </xref> 클래스 이름에 따라 노드를 필터링 할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: 경우에만 탐색기 변경의 상태는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A>메서드가 반환 되었음을 `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next preceding node in reverse document order.
trans-unit.target: 문서와 반대 순서로 다음 이전 노드에서 반복기를 배치합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the next preceding node exists, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: MoveNext 메서드를 설정 하는 다음 선행 노드가 있는 경우는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.Current%2A>속성을 현재 결과 탐색기입니다; 그렇지 않으면는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.Current%2A>속성 변경 되지 않습니다.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingIterator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the next preceding node exists; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>다음 선행 노드가 있으면; 그렇지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.
